+
+## Schedule and retention
+
+The default timer runs daily at `04:30`, with a persistent timer and up to 15
+minutes of randomized delay. Retention is:
+
+- 7 daily snapshots
+- 5 weekly snapshots
+- 12 monthly snapshots
+- 3 yearly snapshots
